item.title: CVE-2017-20127|2024-08-05T21:45:25.951Z -- unspecified -- kb%20login%20authentication%20script
item.description: A vulnerability was found in KB Login Authentication Script 1.1 and classified as critical. Affected by this issue is some unknown functionality. The manipulation of the argument username/password with the input 'or''=' leads to sql injection. The attack may be launched remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
